Description: The 'bnxFortran' package provides some C functions that wrap 
    Fortran algorithms. These interface functions are implemented here to be 
    called directly from the C or C++ source code level of other R packages. 
URL: https://github.com/bionumerix/bnxFortran#readme
BugReports: https://github.com/bionumerix/bnxFortran/issues/new
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
